This documentation describes the Cloudsoft Service Broker tile for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF). You can use Cloudsoft Service Broker to control security and restrict access between your PCF applications and their services and data sources. The following list describes the key features of the tile:

* Securely connect databases and applications within PCF.
* Control service provisioning and access.
* Monitor service and plan usage. 
* Receive security alerts and stop users or apps.

